{
  "stem": "25651.5",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And when we were in the jacuzzi on the balcony in San Salito, above San Francisco, you know, on the other side of the bridge, he says to me and Eve, you must excuse my little girls that they are looking at you strangely, because you are actually the first people outside the family who are with us in the jacuzzi.",
      "word_count": 65
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We weren't even naked.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were-- they always went into the jacuzzi naked.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But this time, we all had swim trunks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, he-- so I said, jokingly I said, well, Karel, what is the [SPEAKING CZECH]?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[SPEAKING CZECH].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What is-- you know, this is quite an honor that we're the first to be in the family jacuzzi.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Why are we deserving of such an honor?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he says, oh, you are deserving because your mother used to feed my mother in Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I said to Eve, you see?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was telling you these stories.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was sort of growing away from my mother, because she was looking after other people.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She wasn't looking after me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The person who was looking after me was Leo and Milos.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So that was stealing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Summer of 1943, there was a big row in the whole of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Eichmann was coming to visit.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there was the opening of this factory where-- I mean, the factory was already going, but he sort of, presumably, came to open the factory where [?",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Traute ?] was working.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there was a row between him and Edelstein.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We didn't know what it was.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
